<!-- FAQ Content -->
<section class="py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">

    <!-- About the Process -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About the Process</h2>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">What is a venture studio and how does it differ from an incubator or accelerator?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">A venture studio builds "our own companies from idea to exit." An incubator or accelerator makes you do the work and they offer business development to startup companies.</p>
      </sl-details>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">How does the process work if I want to pitch an idea?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">You submit through our form. We respond quickly and book a short virtual meeting if the idea feels right. The step after that is a physical meeting.</p>
      </sl-details>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">What types of ideas are you looking for?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Niche digital services that can "scale" and where you have industry knowledge or good insight about a real problem.</p>
      </sl-details>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">What do you mean by niche?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Smaller solutions to an annoying problem. For example, you're in a workflow and it takes enormous time to convert data from one format to another to move information. Or you improve an existing feature in an existing platform.</p>
      </sl-details>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">Does the idea have to be completely unique or can it build on something that already exists?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">It doesn't need to be unique – many winning companies are improvements of something that already works.</p>
      </sl-details>
    </div>

    <!-- About the Collaboration -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About the Collaboration</h2>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">Do I need to know how to code or build the product myself?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">No. That's our role. Your role is to be a subject matter expert and "pilot customer" where you provide initial testing – preferably in a live environment – and then give feedback for modification and further development. We build – you help us hit the mark.</p>
      </sl-details>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">How does ownership and share distribution work in the project?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">As the idea contributor and active participant, you receive "options" in the company formed for the idea.</p>
      </sl-details>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">Can I participate as an active co-owner in the company that's created?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Yes.</p>
      </sl-details>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">What happens if I don't want to or can't engage more than contributing the idea?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Then it's not interesting for us. We need an engaged counterpart with knowledge about the problem to validate the idea.</p>
      </sl-details>
    </div>

    <!-- About Ideas and Intellectual Property -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About Ideas and Intellectual Property</h2>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">How is my idea protected when I share it with you?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">We handle all incoming ideas professionally. Our business model is to work together with people with expertise on a subject. We don't realize any ideas without a person like you who is engaged with deep knowledge and commitment.</p>
      </sl-details>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">Can I submit multiple ideas?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Of course! Send as many as you want.</p>
      </sl-details>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">What happens if someone else submits a similar idea?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">We only invest in the combination of person + knowledge + idea we believe in the most.</p>
      </sl-details>
    </div>

    <!-- About the Selection -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About the Selection</h2>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">How do you choose which ideas to invest in?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">We look at "scalability and market" for the product as well as "knowledge level/competence/personality" for you who submitted the idea.</p>
      </sl-details>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">What's the most common reason an idea doesn't move forward?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">That we don't believe in it.</p>
      </sl-details>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">How long does it take to get a response?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Usually within two weeks.</p>
      </sl-details>
    </div>

    <!-- About the Journey Forward -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About the Journey Forward</h2>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">How long does it take from idea to finished product?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">The goal is 8 weeks.</p>
      </sl-details>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">What are your expectations of me to help find customers and launch?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">You participate as the "first customer case" and serve as a reference.</p>
      </sl-details>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">Can you bring in external investors in the next step?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Yes.</p>
      </sl-details>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">What happens if the project fails?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Then the project is closed down.</p>
      </sl-details>
    </div>

    <!-- About the Idea Provider -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About the Idea Provider</h2>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">Do I need to have a company to participate?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">No.</p>
      </sl-details>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">Does it cost anything for me to pitch an idea?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">No.</p>
      </sl-details>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">Can I be anonymous when I submit an idea?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">No.</p>
      </sl-details>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">Can I pitch as a student, employee, or together with a team?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Absolutely – we welcome everyone.</p>
      </sl-details>
    </div>

    <!-- About Economics & Returns -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About Economics & Returns</h2>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">Do I get any compensation directly when you choose my idea?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">No, the compensation lies in the "ownership."</p>
      </sl-details>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">How much of the company can I expect to own?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Up for discussion depending on your engagement, but it happens through options.</p>
      </sl-details>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">How and when do I make money from my idea?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">When the project becomes a company that is then sold.</p>
      </sl-details>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">How do you view exits or sales of companies started in the studio?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">A sale of the company is always our goal, where we build for exit within 18–24 months.</p>
      </sl-details>
    </div>

    <!-- About Security & Long-term -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About Security & Long-term</h2>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">What happens if I change my mind and want to leave the project?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Then you drop out and your ownership is at risk.</p>
      </sl-details>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">What happens to the code and IP if we end the collaboration?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Everything remains in the company.</p>
      </sl-details>
    </div>

    <!-- About Our Studio -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About Our Studio</h2>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">Why should I choose your venture studio over trying myself?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">There's no faster way to go from idea to product.</p>
      </sl-details>

      <sl-details class="mb-4">
        <div slot="summary" class="text-lg font-semibold">What success stories or cases have you already built?</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">The Gundar team has built and sold several software companies with good results.</p>
      </sl-details>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

